<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢ - بَابُ الضَّادِ الْمُعْجَمَةِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٢٣٩ - ضَاعَ الْعِلْمُ مِنْ بَيْنِ أَفْخَاذِ النِّسَاءِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>هُوَ مِنْ كَلامِ بَعْضِ الْعُلَمَاءِ وَلَيْسَ بِحَدِيثٍ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٢٤٠ - الضَّحِكُ مِنْ غَيْرِ عَجَبٍ مِنْ قِلَّةِ الأَدَبِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>كَلامٌ شَائِعٌ وَلَيْسَ بِحَدِيثٍ نَعَمْ أَخْرَجَ الدَّيْلَمِيُّ حَدِيثَ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٢٤١ - الضَّحِكِ مِنْ غَيْرِ عَجَبٍ مُذْهِبٌ لِلْمُرُوءَةِ مَمْحَقَةٌ لِلرِّزْقِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٢٤٢ - الضَّرُورَاتُ تُبِيحُ الْمَحْظُورَاتِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>